# Files that should NOT be included in the pub.dev package tarball,
# but should remain in the git repository for contributors.

# The top-level `docs/` directory holds design specs, PRDs, and
# internal planning notes. Pub's package-layout convention reserves
# `doc/` (singular) for user-facing API docs, and warns about any
# plural `docs/` directory. Excluding it keeps the published tarball
# small and avoids the warning.
docs/
